{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's nothing-- you don't worry about what is going to happen tomorrow, because you don't know what's happen-- going to happen in half an hour.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's all I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's no time to think about these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Philosophizing, you-- there is no time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You-- you just carry on as best as you can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You line up for your food and then you see where you can wash yourself and maybe you can-- maybe you can visit my parents, and then you are on other duty, or you have to stand here for a [? few ?] hours and watch the people don't cross the bridge, because if they cross the bridge they can beat the queue, which is lined up from there.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there's always something to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or then you have to sleep for a few hours at night, or then it rains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then you have to go under, or you go below.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there's always something to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you reached Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we reached Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the British sent out a-- a-- a-- a tugboat, and they towed us in, because we couldn't do it on our own.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no-- no engine, and no engine power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- they towed us in to port.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The port is Limassol, the big port in Cyprus, and we were--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first thing the British was that they arrested the captain and the whole crew, because you know-- because they were considered smuggling illegal immigrants into British territories.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were immediately arrested, and I don't know what happened to them afterwards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they were tried, and they get a few months in jail or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
